---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="湖心亭看雪" description="把张岱的「上下一白」做成可以划进去的湖。">
  <article class="story" data-fade>
    <header class="story-hero">
      <p class="story-eyebrow">Interactive · 2026</p>
      <h1 class="story-title">湖心亭看雪</h1>
      <p class="story-sub">把「上下一白」做成可以划进去的湖。</p>
    </header>

    <div class="story-body">
      <p>
        张岱写雪，最妙是那几个量词：长堤一痕、湖心亭一点、与余舟一芥、舟中人两三粒。我用 AI 生成了一座三维的雪夜西湖，把这几个「一」做成可以划进去的场景。
      </p>

      <p>
        拖动环顾，空格或长按「划桨」行舟。大雪三日，湖中人鸟声俱绝，你一个人往湖心亭去。
      </p>

      <figure class="story-figure">
        <a href="/snow/" aria-label="进入湖心亭看雪互动场景">
          <img
            src="/projects/snow/card.jpg"
            alt="雪夜西湖：小舟驶向湖心亭"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </a>
      </figure>

      <p>
        <a class="story-link" href="/snow/">独往湖心亭 →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .story {
    padding: 0 96px 160px;
  }

  .story-hero {
    max-width: 768px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 160px 0 72px;
  }

  .story-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 22px;
    letter-spacing: -0.28px;
    color: #707070;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }

  .story-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 60px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 72px;
    letter-spacing: -1.2px;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 60px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 72px;
    letter-spacing: -1.2px;
    color: #707070;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story-body {
    max-width: 768px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .story-body p {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 42px;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    color: #000;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .story-body p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
  }

  .story-figure {
    margin: 48px 0;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .story-figure img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    transition: opacity 200ms;
  }

  .story-figure a:hover img {
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  .story-link {
    color: #000;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 6px;
    transition: color 200ms;
  }

  .story-link:hover {
    color: #707070;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story {
      padding: 0 24px 80px;
    }

    .story-hero {
      padding: 120px 0 56px;
    }

    .story-title,
    .story-sub {
      font-size: 36px;
      line-height: 44px;
      letter-spacing: -0.72px;
    }

    .story-body p {
      font-size: 19px;
      line-height: 33px;
    }

    .story-figure {
      margin: 40px 0;
    }
  }
</style>
